@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Piano Hobby";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - My Piano Hobby</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-JcKb8q3iqJ61gNV9KGb8thSsNjpSL0n8PARn9HuZOnIxN0hoP+VmmDGMN5t9UJ0Z" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.ico">
    <!-- Add your custom CSS styles here -->
    <style>
        /* Add your custom CSS styles */
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to My Piano Hobby Page</h1>
            <img src="~/img/piano.jpeg" alt="Piano Image" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 400px; margin-top: 20px;">
            <img src="~/img/sheetmusicheart.jpeg" alt="Piano Image" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 400px; margin-top: 20px;">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>About My Piano Hobby</h2>
            <p>
                Playing the piano is not just a hobby for me; it's a passion. I have been playing the piano for several years now and it brings me immense joy and satisfaction. The piano allows me to express myself creatively and emotionally through music.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether it's classical pieces by Chopin and Beethoven or modern tunes by contemporary artists, I love exploring various genres and styles on the piano. The feeling of mastering a challenging piece or improvising melodies is incredibly rewarding.
            </p>
            <p>
                Apart from playing solo, I also enjoy collaborating with other musicians and performing in concerts and recitals. The piano has opened doors to new friendships and opportunities, enriching my life in countless ways.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
